---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Huntress Managed Security | Blue Cap IT — Huntress Partner" description="Blue Cap IT partners with Huntress to deliver 24/7 managed cybersecurity. SOC-backed EDR, identity threat detection, SIEM, and security awareness training — purpose-built for SMBs and backed by a world-class Security Operations Center.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> Huntress</div>
      <div class="section-label">Huntress Partner</div>
      <h1>Managed Security. <span class="grad">24/7 Protection.</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Blue Cap IT partners with Huntress to deliver SOC-backed cybersecurity that finds and stops hackers before they cause damage. Managed EDR, identity threat detection, SIEM, and security awareness training — all powered by a 24/7 Security Operations Center with an industry-leading 8-minute mean time to respond.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HUNTRESS LOGO -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:2rem 1.5rem;">
      <img src="/Huntress/huntress-logo-teal.png" alt="Huntress" style="max-height:60px;width:auto;"/>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY HUNTRESS -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Huntress</div>
          <h2>Hackers Don't Sleep.<br/><span class="grad">Neither Does Huntress.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Most cybersecurity tools generate alerts — Huntress actually stops threats. Their 24/7 AI-assisted Security Operations Center investigates every alert, eliminates false positives, and remediates real threats before they cause damage. No alert fatigue. No missed attacks.</p>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">As a Huntress Partner, Blue Cap IT deploys and manages the full Huntress platform for you — so you get enterprise-grade threat detection and response without needing an in-house security team.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🎯</div>
            <div><h4>24/7 SOC-Backed Protection</h4><p>A world-class Security Operations Center monitors your environment around the clock — investigating threats, eliminating false positives, and responding in minutes, not hours.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">⚡</div>
            <div><h4>8-Minute Mean Time to Respond</h4><p>Industry-leading response times mean threats are contained and remediated before hackers can move laterally or cause damage.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🏆</div>
            <div><h4>Award-Winning Platform</h4><p>Winner of the 2026 SC Award for Best Managed Detection and Response Service. Purpose-built for businesses like yours.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔧</div>
            <div><h4>Fully Managed by Blue Cap IT</h4><p>We deploy, configure, and manage Huntress for you. You get complete protection with zero added complexity to your team.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRODUCT LINES -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Huntress Platform</div>
        <h2>Complete Protection.<br/><span class="grad">One Platform.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">Huntress combines endpoint protection, identity security, log management, and human risk reduction into one unified, SOC-managed platform.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;">
        <a href="huntress-edr.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">💻</div>
          <h3>Managed EDR</h3>
          <p>24/7 endpoint detection and response with a lightweight agent, behavioral analytics, and automated threat remediation. The SOC handles everything from detection to cleanup.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="huntress-itdr.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🔐</div>
          <h3>Managed ITDR</h3>
          <p>Identity threat detection and response for Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace. Stops account takeovers, business email compromise, and unauthorized access in 3 minutes.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="huntress-siem.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>Managed SIEM</h3>
          <p>Security information and event management without the complexity. 24/7 threat response and compliance reporting, fully managed by SOC experts at a predictable price.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="huntress-sat.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🎓</div>
          <h3>Security Awareness Training</h3>
          <p>Engaging, expert-backed training built on real-world threat intelligence. Hands-on simulations and gamification that make cybersecurity concepts stick.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
        <h2>Detect. Respond. <span class="grad">Remediate.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">Huntress doesn't just alert you to threats — it eliminates them. Here's how the platform protects your business around the clock.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));">
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🔍</div>
          <h3>1. Continuous Monitoring</h3>
          <p>Lightweight agents and cloud integrations monitor your endpoints, identities, and logs 24/7 for suspicious activity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🤖</div>
          <h3>2. AI + Human Analysis</h3>
          <p>AI-assisted detection flags potential threats. Human SOC analysts validate every alert — eliminating false positives and identifying real attacks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3>3. Rapid Response</h3>
          <p>Confirmed threats are contained and remediated in minutes. Compromised endpoints are isolated, malicious processes are killed, and damage is prevented.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">📋</div>
          <h3>4. Detailed Reporting</h3>
          <p>You get clear, actionable incident reports explaining what happened, what was done, and what to watch for — no jargon, no guesswork.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <div class="section-label">Get Started</div>
      <h2>Ready for <span class="grad">24/7 Protection?</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:600px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT to get Huntress deployed across your organization. We'll assess your security posture and show you how Huntress can protect your business around the clock.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
